</tr><tr><th class="sidebar-heading" style="background:#efefef;">
Phonology</th></tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content" style="padding-bottom:0.6em;">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/English_phonology" title="English phonology">Phonology</a> (<a href="/wiki/Phonological_history_of_English" title="Phonological history of English">History</a>)</li></ul></td>
</tr><tr><th class="sidebar-heading" style="background:#efefef;">
